name: Project Universe
description:
Project Universe is a NEED FOR SPEED fan game developed by the undisclosed White Box studios. Keep in mind the project is in pre-alpha development. 

Project Universe brings all of EA's Black Box Need for Speed titles all into one place, one platform, all online. Rather you'd like to race down the city of Rockport, hit the canyons in Palmont, or even take a cruise in the dark city of Bayview, it's all up to you.
